Add an Intent Filter to manifest

Action  :
    -   A string naming the action to perform ( full string name for the action )
    -   <action>

Data    :
    -   A description of the data associated with the intent (  MIME type, URI prefix, URI scheme )
    -   <data> element

Category:

<activity android:name="ShareActivity">
    <intent-filter>
        <action android:name="android.intent.action.SEND"/>
        <category android:name="android.intent.category.DEFAULT"/>
        <data android:mimeType="text/plain"/>
        <data android:mimeType="image/*"/>
    </intent-filter>
</activity>

can have multiple intent-filter
